Converted by SambaPaTi from the soldier of fortune 2 map tb_high_wire_2
originally by "BRIGZY  [TB MAPZ] <Tim Briggs>"

high buildings with access to all roof tops. The makings of a great sniper war.  High_Wire has two new underground areas to do battle and a tower that soars high into the map giving players sniper access to all building tops. Thats if you can make it to the top on the high wire without getting wasted.
